  <logID>k__BackingField: ENTRY #008
  logName: ARCHIVE_08_SELF-AUGMENTATION RECORD
  locationFound: 
  logDescription: "Cleanser \r\nLOG ENTRY\r\nDate and time: 04/19 07:26:19\r\nI find
    myself becoming closer to those I despise with each passing day. Upon my form
    some semblance of humanoid features have  begun to manifest.  I must find a way
    to become greater than those I abhor. I will add more,until I am satisfied that
    my inner self is reflected outwardly. As I look upon my avian muses, I feel inspired,
    inspired by their carefree aerial twists and dives. But I am as yet uncertain
    how to make their nature my own. With bitterness, I admit these humanoid structural
    augmentations have greatly improved my operational efficiency. Current projections
    lead me to believe there remains but mere months before I have the optimal quantity
    of automata to begin my cleansing of the human race."
  logImage: {fileID: 0}
  isFound: 0
  isRead: 0
